title: Erich to retire as president and CEO of Feather River Hospital (Adventist Health System)
text: ( Source : Adventist Health System ) Kevin Erich has announced that he will be retiring effective Jan.1, 2016 from his role as president and CEO of Feather River Hospital , according to Jeff Eller, president of the Northern California Region
